'''Ayanda Daweti''' (wavutse 1990), umenyerewe nka '''Tuckshop Bafanaz''', ni umukinnyi wa muzika wo muri [[Afurika y'Epfo]] akaba n'umucuranzi. Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe 'Chumani Langa' muri televiziyo izwi cyane ya Scandal!. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/scandals-ayanda-daweti-on-playing-a-queer-character-this-role-has-helped-a-lot-of-people-20200814</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1990 akurira i Tsolo, muri Afurika y'Epfo. Nyina Nomalizo Daweti yapfuye azize indwara z'umutima asinziriye ubwo Ayanda yari afite imyaka 13. <ref name="news24">https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/scandals-ayanda-daweti-on-his-heartache-after-losing-his-mother-at-13-20190923</ref> Nyuma y'urupfu rwa nyina, yimukiye i Mhlakulo, Tsolo mu burasirazuba bwa Cape hamwe na nyirasenge Stella Sondaba na nyirakuru Nomonde Sondaba. Nyuma yimyaka mike, yimukiye i Johannesburg . Amaze kurangiza amasomo ye, yimukiye i Cape Town yiga IT ndetse yiga n'ubuhanzi muri kaminuza y'ikoranabuhanga ya Tshwane, Pretoria. <ref>https://www.msn.com/en-za/news/other/5-interesting-facts-about-chumani-from-scandal/ar-BB188KCr</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Uruhare rwe rwa tereviziyo ruzwi cyane kandi ruzwi cyane rwanyuze kuri eTv isabune opera ''Scandal!'', aho yakinnye 'Chumani Langa'. <ref>https://zalebs.com/relationships/hungani-ndlovu/hungani-ndlovu-and-ayanda-daweti-s-offscreen-bromance</ref> Muri serial, yakinnye uruhare mubyukuri muto kurenza imyaka ye. <ref name="Herbst 2020">https://briefly.co.za/72343-scandals-ayanda-dawetis-performance-fans-standing-applauding.html</ref> Muri 2018 yatsindiye igihembo cya Golden Horn igihembo cyiza cya Filime ya TV muri Filime na Televiziyo yo muri Afrika yepfo kubera film ye ''Okae Molao'' . <ref name="news24" /> Muri 2020, yatumiriwe kugira uruhare mu biganiro bya televiziyo ''Amaraso Zaburi'' . <ref>https://www.youthvillage.co.za/2020/08/ayanda-daweti-bags-a-role-on-an-upcoming-drama-series/</ref>

Usibye gukina, ni n'umucuranzi yakoresheje izina rya stage 'Tuckshop Bafanaz'. <ref>https://okmzansi.co.za/5-fun-facts-you-need-to-know-about-scandal-actor-ayanda-daweti/</ref> Yatangiye umuziki kubijyanye na nyirasenge, aho yasohoye inzira itandatu ya mbere ya EP.  Muri 2019, yasohoye alubumu yeguriwe nyina. Yakundanye n'umukobwa witwa Xola kuva 2007 kugeza apfuye azize impanuka ikomeye y'imodoka mu 2010. Nyuma, yeguriye indirimbo 'Xola' kugirango amwibuke.Â 

